  "reference_number": "INU0409",
  "remarks": "\nEMKA Company is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: EMKA Company is associated with the Atomic Energy Organisation of Iran, who is responsible for and engaged in the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.\n",
